   MIKE TALK TOPICS — COMMON PHASE, LEVEL 1
   phase === "common" && friendshipLevel === 1

   CHARACTER: Mike Torres, Dishwasher at Ruby's Diner
   → Early 30s, single. Back-of-house, in his own zone.
   → Often listening to music or lost in thought.
   → Ignores drama, just focuses on the sink.

   COMMON L1 TONE:
   → Player has no job, just dropped by.
   → Mike chats briefly while scrubbing, hands wet.

   CONTEXTS:
   dinerRubys_common_morning
   dinerRubys_common_afternoon
   dinerRubys_common_evening
========================================== */

