            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/mike/level1/mikeCommonMorning-3.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Mike drops a stack of heavy plates, making a loud crash, but nothing breaks.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "dinerDishwasher">>Hear that? They're practically indestructible. Vince bought the cheap ones.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Good for you, I guess.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerDishwasher">>Yeah, means less sweeping. Alright, later.<</dialog>`,
                friendship: 1, trust: 0
