            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/mike/level1/mikeCommonAfternoon-1.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Mike gestures vaguely with a soapy sponge at a huge pile of dishes.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "dinerDishwasher">>Lunch rush. The worst invention in human history.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>It looks like a nightmare.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerDishwasher">>It is. Everyone eats at exactly noon. Why not 1:30? Idiots.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>I'll let you work.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerDishwasher">>Good call.<</dialog>`,
                friendship: 1, trust: 0
