<<dialog "dinerDishwasher">>Waste. Too much waste. People order sides they don't even touch.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>At least you don't have to clean it.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerDishwasher">>Just throw it out. But it's still stupid. See ya.<</dialog>`,
