            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/mike/level1/mikeCommonAfternoon-3.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Mike takes a quick drink from a water bottle sitting dangerously close to the sink.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "dinerDishwasher">>Steamy in here today. The dishwasher runs so hot it's basically a sauna.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Drink plenty of water.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerDishwasher">>Trying. The steam's getting to my lungs though.<</dialog>
<<dialog "player">>Don't pass out.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerDishwasher">>I'll try not to.<</dialog>`,
